headline: Revvity Expands Alliance with Genomics England to Drive Research into Newborn Genomic Sequencing in England
summary: WALTHAM, Mass., March 20, 2025--Revvity announced an agreement with Genomics England to further collaborate on the Generation Study by providing sequencing services.
